        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nTwo of the changes affect behavior of the code.  They ought to be in a change ticket by themselves.\n1) using replace, not replaceAll in CUI.java\n2) print stack to stdout (via java util logging) instead of stderr (via e.printStackTrace) to report startup error in AAF_GUI.java\n\nAlso, a lesser concern, the exception handling in AAF_GUI.Main is unnecessarily nested.  I suggest sequential try blocks.",
